==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: dā'drēmˈ
===Noun===
'''daydream''' ([[daydreams]])

#pleasant thought that one has while awake, especially when that thought is unrelated to what one is doing at the time, such as romance

====Translations====
* Dutch: [[dagdroom]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

#to think about something pleasant while awake, especially about things unrelated to what one is doing at the time, such as romance
#:''Stop daydreaming and get back to work!''

